title: Reel Rock 10 Movie Viewing
text:
Reel Rock 10 Movie Viewing Where 
7:30 p.m. Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 Categories 
Events, Movies | Film, Outdoors | Recreation Sender Films and Big UP Productions bring San Diego a mind-blowing, palm-sweating pump-fest of climbing flicks for the 10th annual REEL ROCK Film Tour. The Reel Rock Film Tour takes audiences to the boundary of what is thought possible. From the worldâ€™s longest free solos, to the most demanding sport climbs these are heart-pounding tales of superhuman skill and determination. It's all part of the cinematic tour de force that is REEL ROCK X. Check http://reelrocktour.com/ to check out the films. Brought to you by UC San Diego Outback Adventures, University Centers and the Allied Climbers of San Diego (ACSD). $1 from each ticket sold goes to the ACSD.
